<mjml>
  <mj-include path="./sub/head.mjml" />
  <mj-body>
    <mj-include path="./sub/header.mjml" />
    <mj-spacer height="20px" />
    <mj-include path="./sub/banner.mjml" />
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column width="600px">
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
        <mj-text mj-class="title_text" align="left">
          Hello,
          <%= target_name %>,
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-text mj-class="body_text" align="left">
          <%= recipient_name %> has commented on your post. Check it out and keep interacting and sharing new content in a form of short posts, articles or videos. Or just have fun with the TWAAmojisâ€¦ Sometimes they sum it up!
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="body_text" align="left">
          Once you log in check out TWAA Books and upload your books if you are an author or if not upload your favourite books for others to find.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="body_text" align="left">
          And if you are a public speaker check out the Twaa Speakers and put up your profile for global stages to find you.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="body_text" align="left">
          We are thrilled to have you onboard as one of our powerful forces on our journey to propel women to greatness.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text mj-class="body_text" align="left">
          Warm Regards, The TWAA team
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="10px" />
        <mj-button href="#" mj-class="btn_twaagold" align="center">
          View Post
        </mj-button>
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-include path="./sub/footer.mjml" />
  </mj-body>
</mjml>